 Out\")</small>\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Stunt Coordination for a Comedy Series or Variety Program|Outstanding Stunt Coordination for a Comedy Series or Variety Program]]\n| Christopher Place\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=2|[[45th Saturn Awards|Saturn Awards]]\n| colspan=\"2\"|Best Streaming Fantasy, Sci-Fi, or Action/Thriller Television Series\n| {{nom}}\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web |last1=Mancuso |first1=Vinnie |title='Avengers: Endgame', 'Game of Thrones' Lead the 2019 Saturn Awards Nominations |url=http://collider.com/saturn-awards-nominations-2019/ |website=Collider |accessdate=July 17, 2019 |date=July 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Actress in a Streaming Presentation \n| [[Natasha Lyonne]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| align=\"center\"|[[Gotham Independent Film Awards 2019|Gotham Awards]]\n| [[Gotham Independent Film Award for Breakthrough Series \u2013 Short Form|Breakthrough Series \u2013 Short Form]]\n| ''Russian Doll''\n| {{nom}}\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/gotham-award-winners-2019-list-full-1258785/ |title='Marriage Story' Sweeps Gotham Awards; Full Winners List |website=The Hollywood Reporter |date=December 2, 2019 |accessdate=December 5, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"| [[24th Satellite Awards|Satellite Awards]]\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Television Series \u2013 Musical or Comedy|Best Musical or Comedy Series]]\n| ''Russian Doll''\n| {{nom}}\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.awardscircuit.com/2019/12/03/24th-satellite-awards-announce-nominations-ford-v-ferrari-leads-the-way/ |title=24th Satellite Awards Announce Nominations, \u2018Ford v Ferrari\u2019 Leads the Way |website=Awards Circuit |first=Karen M. |last=Peterson |date=December 3, 2019 |accessdate=December 6, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Actress \u2013 Television Series Musical or Comedy|Best Actress in a Mus